{"tid":1310093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］Cash Out Challenge","createTime":"2019-07-12T13:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:07:00.000Z","uid":265092,"like":167,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"2313937382175e17df932e2173e33b268797d155","tid":1310093,"uid":265092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"為響應713全民撳錢中銀送中活動，小弟決定將行動升級，發動 #CashOutChallenge<br />\n<br />\n玩法好簡單，大家為手上現金拍照，上傳到社交媒體，並提名三人，被提名的人需要在24小時內上傳一張現金照片，如此類推。<br />\n<br />\n而拒絕接受挑戰者，需要捐款到援助抗爭的組織及媒體（例如星火、立場新聞、民陣等等），多多益善少少無拘。<br />\n<br />\n記住，單單從一間銀行撳錢然後存入另一間銀行並無實際效用，我們必須手持現金，尤其是美元現金，才能引發一系列骨牌效應，撼動銀行體系，削弱政府談判力量，政府才會正面回應群眾。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n全民撳錢，直搗糧倉！<br />\n<br />\n#金融投爭<br />\n#HKDtoUSD<br />\n#CashOutChallenge<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCK5FBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCK5FBk.png&h=e5ceaafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d771523f880ca9bb34bdaf8fca1d95e67367bce","tid":1310093,"uid":265092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbd29793e803e6093d7e66f811f8f87e360f2ef","tid":1310093,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"叉撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c363df70bc4cdeaf9cdc84c3158719a62d048298","tid":1310093,"uid":265092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"撳撚到佢乾塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796f559ac30d59b6d50b01c2de35f244a825215f","tid":1310093,"uid":265092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"一個人撳第二個又撳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" clas